title: Jessica Kirson: Jersey Class
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with great Jessica Kirson. Jessica talks growing up in New Jersey, having divorced parents, and stand up comedy. You know Jessica From Comedy Central, The Tonight Show, and her own stand up special.
